諗？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"99a01a7f2106b8645df02945ca873e40a06c3719","tid":1632629,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:09:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32bc8a8e27eb5533ef0ae192a89998f1625b8ea7","tid":1632629,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:17:17.000Z","msg":"推 ！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2918f84c756b4af7163af333170079f1f15bef","tid":1632629,"uid":14435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:29:23.000Z","msg":"個諗法唔錯 不過身材要有返咁上下先睇得到成段字喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉做口號會唔會仲好"},{"pid":"cdf8a418942fd8520c4d62ba23e07c5f121cf8df","tid":1632629,"uid":280341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c2918f84c756b4af7163af333170079f1f15bef","tid":1632629,"uid":14435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:29:23.000Z","msg":"個諗法唔錯 不過身材要有返咁上下先睇得到成段字喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉做口號會唔會仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:54:36.000Z","msg":"其實我目的係popo濫捕時，記者影住，任何人都可以見到黑底白字大大聲讀俾POPO聽，令藍絲及中立派知道其實所有野都有法可循，唔係我地9up,道理其實一直係我地呢邊。而家所有衝突都係由popo濫捕而引起，製造輿論。"}]}